casebody.data:
Askari Abdullah MUHAMMAD, petitioner,
v.
Michael D. CREWS, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections, et al. No. 13-7624, 13A649. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2014.

*894Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
